through this transition with limited solutions, outside of HRT.\"","author":"Dr. Mariza Snyder, D.C. - Women's Health Expert& Best-selling Author","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_39.png"}},"testimonial_3DP9Q7":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"quote":"“Berkeley Life is a company that has gained my respect for their commitment to the development of science-based products that modulate Nitric Oxide status and function. Their commitment to scientific rigor and innovative solutions makes them a powerful ally in the pursuit of functional health.”","author":"Dr. Jeffrey Bland, PhD - Nutritional Biochemist & Functional Medicine Pioneer","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_39_0fbed095-15dd-4860-b51b-2d2a8e3cbd79.png"}},"testimonial_ApdPgd":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"quote":"“Blood flow and healing are critical to the success of our treatments, and the integration of Nitric Oxide has really helped. We continue to promote Berkeley’s N.O. for all of our body procedures as well as men presenting to our men's clinic – our patients are loving the results.”","author":"Dr. Richard Moore, MD - Internal Medicine Physician","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_39_1.png"}}},"block_order":["testimonial_VaaCMk","testimonial_3DP9Q7","testimonial_ApdPgd"],"name":"C Expert Trust","settings":{"title_prefix":"Trusted By Top Experts.","title_highlight":"Everywhere.","badge_logo":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Clinicians_Choice.svg","badge_text":"<p><strong>307 clinicians<\/strong> share Berkeley Life on FrontrowMD without compensation.<\/p>","badge_avatars":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_93490f6f-2f47-4aa0-960d-1150a22b62d7.svg","badge_link_text":"Read their Reviews","badge_link_url":"","show_reviews_inline":true,"reviews_product_type":"nitric-oxide","bg_color":"#f6f3f0","text_color":"#2b2e38","accent_color":"#d15234","card_bg_color":"#1b1e2a","card_text_color":"#ffffff","badge_bg_color":"#ebe8e6","pagination_color":"#ffffff","pagination_active_color":"#d54f2f","padding_top":4,"padding_bottom":4}},"1782905455d7a8a335":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"okendo_reviews_widget_C8kx8z":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/okendo\/blocks\/reviews-widget\/bb689e69-ea70-4661-8fb7-ad24a2e23c29","settings":{"product":"","widget_type":"reviews_widget"}}},"block_order":["okendo_reviews_widget_C8kx8z"],"settings":{}},"c_content_text_Kjcnpf":{"type":"c-content-text","name":"C Content Text","settings":{"desktop_layout":"row-reverse","mobile_layout":"column-reverse","image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/mbg-lp.webp","heading_1":"This Isn't a Supplement Just for How You Feel Right Now.","heading_2_italic":"It's a Foundation for What's to Come.","text":"<p>You're already doing the work. Eating well. Moving. Prioritizing sleep. And yet something has shifted — in your energy, your clarity, your heart health — in ways that don't respond to the things that used to work. That shift has a biological explanation. Nitric Oxide production declines steadily with age and faster during hormonal transitions like perimenopause and menopause. And Nitric Oxide governs the vascular function that underlies nearly everything you're trying to protect. <\/p><p>Berkeley Life Nitric Oxide Support is clinically studied to restore healthy NO production — the pathway perimenopause puts under pressure. And the test strips let you measure your levels before you start and again in 90 minutes, so you don't have to take anyone's word for it. You see it - then you feel it.<\/p>","btn_variant":"pill","btn_label":"","btn_link":"","btn_bg_color":"#d15234","btn_text_color":"#ffffff","btn_show_arrow":false,"btn_2_variant":"underline","btn_2_label":"","btn_2_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/nitric-oxide-support","btn_2_bg_color":"#d15234","btn_2_text_color":"#d15234","btn_2_show_arrow":false,"bg_color":"#f6f3f0","text_color":"#1b1c29","highlight_color":"#d15234","padding_top":4,"padding_bottom":4}},"c_blocks_dropdown_8ffbiU":{"type":"c-blocks-dropdown","blocks":{"system_card_gNVMkN":{"type":"system_card","settings":{"title":"CARDIOVASCULAR HEALTH","subtitle":"Your vascular system is under more pressure than ever.","description":"<p>Estrogen decline reduces N.O. — the molecule your blood vessels need to stay flexible and open. Berkeley Life supports healthy blood pressure and arterial function as cardiovascular risk starts to rise.*\u2028<br\/><br\/><strong>12.5 pts <\/strong>avg. reduction in systolic blood pressure in the clinical trial.*<\/p>","use_cormorant_strong":true}},"system_card_cwnWCA":{"type":"system_card","settings":{"title":"ENERGY & ENDURANCE","subtitle":"Not a motivation problem. A delivery problem.","description":"<p>N.O. governs how efficiently your cells receive oxygen. When it declines, energy declines with it. Berkeley Life restores that system.*<br\/><br\/><strong>300%<\/strong> increase in capacity to produce energy after 3 months.*<\/p>","use_cormorant_strong":true}},"system_card_RKxNHB":{"type":"system_card","settings":{"title":"COGNITIVE FUNCTION","subtitle":"Brain fog after 40 is a blood flow issue.","description":"<p>Cerebral blood flow depends directly on N.O. When it drops, so does mental sharpness. Berkeley Life supports the vascular foundation your brain runs on.*\u2028<br\/><br\/><strong>28%<\/strong> improvement in circulation — the gold standard measure of blood flow.*<\/p>","use_cormorant_strong":true}},"system_card_WYqBnd":{"type":"system_card","settings":{"title":"RECOVERY","subtitle":"You're putting in the work. Your recovery should reflect that.","description":"<p>Oxygen delivery to muscle tissue is a N.O. function. When it declines, recovery slows. Berkeley Life supports faster recovery and sustained endurance.*\u2028\u2028<br\/><br\/><strong>300% <\/strong>increase in capacity to produce energy after 3 months in a published clinical trial.*<\/p>","use_cormorant_strong":true}}},"block_order":["system_card_gNVMkN","system_card_cwnWCA","system_card_RKxNHB","system_card_WYqBnd"],"name":"C Blocks Dropdown","settings":{"heading_1":"One Molecule.","heading_2_highlight":"Five Systems.","subtext":"Two capsules a day. Clinically validated Nitric Oxide support for the systems that drive how you feel, perform, and age.","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/block-dropdowns.webp","primary_btn_label":"","primary_btn_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/nitric-oxide-support","secondary_btn_label":"","secondary_btn_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/the-science","bg_color":"#ffffff","heading_color":"#1b1c29","highlight_color":"#d95c3c","text_color":"#1b1c29","card_bg_color":"#f6f5f3","card_title_color":"#d95c3c","card_text_color":"#333333","btn_primary_bg":"#d95c3c","btn_primary_text":"#ffffff","btn_secondary_border":"#ffffff","btn_secondary_text":"#ffffff","padding_top":5,"padding_bottom":5}},"1739199459aacb5165":{"type":"apps","settings":{}},"c_split_card_dbHhWm":{"type":"c-split-card","custom_css":[".c-font-cormorant-title {font-style: italic;}"],"name":"C Split Card","settings":{"custom_id":"","product":"nitric-oxide-test-strips","title":"Your Wearable Can't Track This, \nBut This Test Strip Can","description":"<p>Berkeley Life Nitric Oxide Test Strips give you a real baseline — the same measurement method used in clinical research — in 10 seconds at home.<br\/>No lab. No appointment. No guesswork.\u2028Check your baseline before you start. Check again in 90 minutes. \u2028Your wearable tracks your steps, your sleep, your heart rate. But Nitric Oxide?<br\/>That's been a blind spot. Until now.<br\/>Set your baseline today.<br\/>Most people see a sustained measurable difference <strong>within a month.*<\/strong><\/p>","btn_text":"Get Your Exclusive NO Kit","btn_link":"#new-offer","btn_show_arrow":true,"btn_bg_color":"#d54f2f","btn_text_color":"#ffffff","title_color":"#d54f2f","text_color":"#2d2d2d","card_bg_color":"#ffffff","border_color":"#d54f2f","section_bg_color":"","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"interactive_graph_xeNQDi":{"type":"interactive-graph","settings":{"custom_id":"","title":"Are Your Nitric Oxide Levels <br>\u2028**Holding You Back?**","paragraph":"NO naturally declines with age — by 50% by age 40, and continues dropping every decade. This invisible drop affects energy, heart health, and how every organ in your body performs.","subtext":"At 40, NO levels plummet, driving weight gain, mood swings, and poor sleep during perimenopause.","gender_select_order":"women_first","bg_color":"#f6f3f0","text_color":"#080b2b"}},"c_marquee_bar_VejMaG":{"type":"c-marquee-bar","blocks":{"item_pCKhD6":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Blood Flow","icon_size":24}},"item_9j9E9z":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Hormonal Balance","icon_size":24}},"item_XUWJza":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Blood Pressure","icon_size":24}},"item_faWDaB":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Circulation","icon_size":24}},"item_3PXCbJ":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Energy","icon_size":24}},"item_9GkmFe":{"type":"item","settings":{"text":"Sexual Health","icon_size":24}}},"block_order":["item_pCKhD6","item_9j9E9z","item_XUWJza","item_faWDaB","item_3PXCbJ","item_9GkmFe"],"name":"C Marquee Bar","settings":{"bg_color":"#d54f2f","text_color":"#ffffff","eyebrow":"Essential for","font_style":"serif","divider":"·","fade_edges":false,"speed":30,"direction":"left","pause_on_hover":true,"padding_top":16,"padding_bottom":16}},"c_real_results_reviews_yQYVqy":{"type":"c-real-results-reviews","blocks":{"video_review_7UdBce":{"type":"video_review","settings":{"video_cdn_url":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/videos\/c\/o\/v\/d7387fadc2e348a2a29bbb3067ccf574.mp4","author_name":""}},"video_review_Y8pTNb":{"type":"video_review","settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/BerkeleyLife2 (1).MP4","video_cdn_url":"","author_name":""}},"video_review_DY4bGk":{"type":"video_review","settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/UGC_Jenna_NO Support.mp4","video_cdn_url":"","author_name":""}},"video_review_QqcXRw":{"type":"video_review","settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/Berkeley Life_ Your Secret to Health & 